{"tid":1125364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"昂山素姬：中國是緬甸榜樣　無國家勤奮上能超越中國","createTime":"2019-04-25T15:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T16:28:19.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1c66b7db867f9ebf5043701b8467036c2bb5cfdd","tid":1125364,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:52:25.000Z","msg":"緬甸國務資政昂山素姬在北京出席第二屆「一帶一路」峰會，內地傳媒《新京報》及澎湃新聞引述昂山素姬在論壇上表示，中國是緬甸的榜樣，證明有決心、努力與勤奮最後能夠得到什麼，世界上沒有任何一個國家在勤奮上能超越中國。<br />\n<br />\n昂山素姬在國際合作高峰論壇「民心相通」分論壇上致辭，稱今次帶着友誼而來，沒有相互信任和理解，就不會有真正的友誼與合作，希望在相互信任和理解的基礎上建立合作和友誼關係，而不是一種以影響力和權力為基礎的合作。她又稱，歡迎各國人民擁抱和迎接各種各樣的文化，為人類發展作貢獻。"},{"pid":"91d7d7f0e2ec35439ea11b4736343d0c17cdd86f","tid":1125364,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190425/s00004/51e51348ba772e6675e0833c1cf42f9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190425%2Fs00004%2F51e51348ba772e6675e0833c1cf42f9f.jpg&h=3f51261a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20190425/s00004/1556204080262/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20190425%2Fs00004%2F1556204080262%2F&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreKbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=cd540ba8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20190425%2Fs00004%2F1556204080262%2F&h=daf41981\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20190425/s00004/1556204080262/</a>"},{"pid":"4e42941d4705d3c918bbaa1ce45818894435e8cb","tid":1125364,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:53:36.000Z","msg":"<del>勤奮</del>奴性"},{"pid":"0ccf9c7086934fa5b2b1aa789d7b240b3b0f36fe","tid":1125364,"uid":50386,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T16:08:09.000Z","msg":"緬甸版777<img src=\"/